---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Read the Aetas Global Innovation privacy policy.">
  <section class="py-24 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
      <p>Last updated: July 11, 2026</p>
      <p>Aetas Global Innovation ("we", "us", or "our") operates the unified brand website at Aetas.ai. This policy details our protocols on data logging, information collections, and data protection rules in compliance with enterprise requirements.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-8">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you submit via our contact forms, AI workflow inquiries, and Advisor Quiz, such as name, email, company name, and specific workflow challenges.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-8">2. How We Use Data</h2>
      <p>We use submitted inputs to route requests to the correct MSSP, MSP, BPO, or AI workflow team and follow up on service inquiries.</p>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-8">3. Information Protection</h2>
      <p>We use reasonable administrative, technical, and organizational safeguards designed to protect submitted information. Any formal certification claims should be verified before being published publicly.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
